title: Prang (Formerly SunWorks) Construction Paper, 10 Assorted Colors, 12" x 18", 100 Sheets
description: SunWorks Heavyweight Construction Paper is made from groundwood and is manufactured by a chemical-free process for a cleaner environment. Paper with high-strength fiber facilitates clean cuts and can be folded evenly without any cracks. Magenta. Assorted colors include: Scarlet, Black, Brown, Pink, Violet, Blue, Holiday Green, Yellow, Yellow-Orange and White. Sold as 100 sheets measuring 12 x 18 inches.
